{"tid":2121404,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【知法犯法】鄧家彪再被爆除罩聚餐慶回歸 攜長者遊新界 三度涉違例","createTime":"2020-07-23T09:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T13:15:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":522,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":118,"replies":[{"pid":"dfb8aa949fd22ff1aa3792c2230d8e0071f76472","tid":2121404,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:30:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200723/DJKZA3EITWDOT7KZZLSQQDPWDA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2FDJKZA3EITWDOT7KZZLSQQDPWDA%2F&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=edaba4e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2FDJKZA3EITWDOT7KZZLSQQDPWDA%2F&h=48197500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200723/DJKZA3EITWDOT7KZZLSQQDPWDA/</a><br />\n<br />\n昨日（22日）工聯會被揭月初在黃大仙富臨皇宮舉行慶回歸晚宴時，容許賓客在進食以外時間脫下口罩四處交談甚至上台唱歌跳舞，涉嫌違反法例《預防及控制疾病規例》第599F章。《蘋果》接獲讀者爆料，當日列席的工聯會鄧家彪，7月4日及5日先後出席另一個慶回歸西式自助餐，以及「千名義工新界一日遊」，同樣不戴口罩與賓客交流及用咪高峰講話，席上餐枱亦沒有1.5米距離。《蘋果》再向鄧多番致電，截稿前沒回覆。"},{"pid":"954aba444f723d76ef220e7d5ab52e895351cedb","tid":2121404,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b30ff79fab3e358d952425aea0279e8656439ec","tid":2121404,"uid":240362,"like":97,"dislike":1,"score":96,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:31:39.000Z","msg":"根據當時的防疫規定，雖然食肆每枱餐桌人數沒上限，但仍然要求每枱間距最少1.5米，顧客在進食以外的時間亦要戴口罩。換言之，鄧家彪7月2日至5日最少3度涉嫌違反法例。《蘋果》截稿前沒接獲鄧家彪回覆。"},{"pid":"99fe82745083c96a787420dfbac84715734fa7bd","tid":2121404,"uid":171094,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:31:43.000Z","msg":"犯法就係犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.